# --- Azure Application Insights — online bug monitoring (/qa-monitoring) -------
# vcst-qa = platform/backend, vcst-qa-storefront = storefront (workspace-based /
# LogAnalytics ingestion). Subscription/RG/resource-names are identifiers
# (committed here). AUTH is AAD-first — your Azure login covers it, NO API key
# needed; keys are an optional fallback in .env.local (see .env.example).
AZURE_SUBSCRIPTION_ID=973d0b8c-44bf-438d-a4b7-1c4162d3ccba
AZURE_RESOURCE_GROUP=vcst
APPINSIGHTS_RESOURCE_BACKEND=vcst-qa
APPINSIGHTS_RESOURCE_STOREFRONT=vcst-qa-storefront
# App IDs resolved via Azure Resource Graph 2026-06-05
# (Portal path: resource → Configure → API Access → "Application ID").
